definition.value: An organic cation obtained by protonation of GGTI-2133 free base.
An organic disulfide obtained by oxidative dimerisation of 1-sulfanylnaphthalen-2-ol.
A beta-hydroxy ketone that is 5-hydroxydecan-3-one substituted by a 4-hydroxy-3-methoxyphenyl moiety at position 1; believed to inhibit adipogenesis. It is a constituent of fresh ginger.
